{"image_id": "KEY_2014_page_185", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "KeyBank’s long-term senior unsecured credit rating is currently four ratings above noninvestment grade at", "bbox": [162.5, 159.1, 1053.5, 179.9]}, {"text": "Moody’s and S&P. If KeyBank’s ratings had been downgraded below investment grade as of December 31,", "bbox": [162.5, 184.1, 1063.2, 204.9]}, {"text": "2014, payments of up to $5 million would have been required to either terminate the contracts or post additional", "bbox": [162.5, 209.1, 1098.5, 229.9]}, {"text": "collateral for those contracts in a net liability position, taking into account all collateral already posted. If", "bbox": [162.5, 234.1, 1039.5, 254.9]}, {"text": "KeyCorp’s ratings had been downgraded below investment grade as of December 31, 2014, payments of less", "bbox": [162.5, 259.1, 1072.5, 279.9]}, {"text": "than $1 million would have been required to either terminate the contracts or post additional collateral for those", "bbox": [162.5, 284.1, 1094.3, 304.9]}, {"text": "contracts in a net liability position, taking into account all collateral already posted.", "bbox": [162.5, 309.1, 858.5, 329.9]}, {"text": "9. Mortgage Servicing Assets", "bbox": [483.2, 374.3, 791.8, 399.3]}, {"text": "We originate and periodically sell commercial mortgage loans but continue to service those loans for the buyers.", "bbox": [162.5, 422.4, 1102.3, 443.2]}, {"text": "We also may purchase the right to service commercial mortgage loans for other lenders. We record a servicing", "bbox": [162.5, 447.4, 1086.5, 468.2]}, {"text": "asset if we purchase or retain the right to service loans in exchange for servicing fees that exceed the going", "bbox": [162.5, 472.4, 1054.6, 493.2]}, {"text": "market servicing rate and are considered more than adequate compensation for servicing. Changes in the carrying", "bbox": [162.5, 497.4, 1110.7, 518.2]}, {"text": "amount of mortgage servicing assets are summarized as follows:", "bbox": [162.5, 52